// Syncthing ignore rules for the ProjectX project folder.
// Prevents native binaries, build artifacts, and generated state from being
// synced between machines — syncing them causes architecture mismatches
// (e.g. macOS arm64 .node files landing on a Windows x64 host) and race
// conditions that silently overwrite working files.
//
// Format: see https://docs.syncthing.net/users/ignoring.html

// Node dependencies — must be installed per-machine
**/node_modules

// Build / dist outputs — regenerated per-machine
**/dist
**/dist-electron
**/build
**/release
**/.next

// Native / platform caches
**/.gradle
**/.dart_tool
**/.pub-cache

// Runtime data (databases, logs, tunnel pid files)
server/data
**/*.db
**/*.db-journal
**/*.db-wal
**/*.db-shm

// OS and editor junk
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo

// Secrets — never sync these between machines
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local
